							<p class="describe">客户可根据业务需求进行个性化排序配置，从而优化搜索效果</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-2">
					<div class="panel panel-define query">
						<div class="panel-heading">
							<h3 class="panel-title">查询功能丰富</h3>
