						</div>
						<div class="panel-body">
							<p class="">
								<img src="images/portal/search.png" alt="智能语义搜索">
							</p>
							<p class="describe">基于多年积累的知识库，提供垂直领域智能语义搜索</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
